description:
This is a 47 minute workout called '45 Min Full Body Cardio HIIT | ALL STANDING | Burn up to 600 Calories, No Repeat, No Equipment' from the channel Eleni Fit.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Ready for another sweaty All Standing HIIT Session? It's a full body Cardio workout with lots of fun and intense exercises. Let's get sweaty! #fullbodyburn #allstanding #fun

*The number of calories you burn will vary from person to person but this might serve as a guideline. 

❀Full Body Workout
❀Time: 45 sec on/ 15 sec off
